Ikut aku sekarang.

322
00:44:49,666 --> 00:44:51,375
Berikan tanganmu. Ayo.

323
00:44:51,875 --> 00:44:53,791
- Siapa kau?
- Tak penting.

324
00:44:54,291 --> 00:44:55,166
Tolong!

325
00:44:55,666 --> 00:44:57,125
Aku sedang menolongmu.

326
00:44:57,125 --> 00:44:58,458
Kau menyakitiku.

327
