407
00:54:53,416 --> 00:54:54,333
Kau lihat?

408
00:55:14,625 --> 00:55:15,833
Sudah dekat.

409
00:55:16,875 --> 00:55:19,208
Malam ini, kau bisa tidur di ranjangmu.

410
00:55:21,291 --> 00:55:22,541
Bagaimana?

411
